 UltraStats Readme
 ----------------------------------

 Welcome to UltraStats, a powerfull parser gamelogs created 
 by for Call of Duty gameservers.


 Support Games
 ----------------------------------
 - Call of Duty
 - Call of Duty: United Offense
 - Call of Duty 2
 - Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare
 - Call of Duty 5: World at War


